{
  "stem": "7437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my mother was already making plans how we would keep in touch because that evening, my sister was to be picked up and transported to her hiding place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She did go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My mother came home from work by herself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, in a way, it was a step in the right direction to save our lives.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "A few days later, my mother came back from work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And until then, she didn't hear anything about my sister, which meant she got to the place where she was supposed to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And a few days later, my mother came home, and we ate our meager meal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she told me to put on the best clothes I still had and not to forget the jacket that had a little bit of jewelry sewed in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She packed two little bundles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And she kept telling me where we were going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were going to be hidden by a farmer with whom my mother dealt before the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We used to buy butter and all sorts of dairy products.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I knew these people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I mean, I knew the, the, the farmer quite well because he lived on a farm across the river on Skobelka.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That's the village that we were going to go to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And so after we ate our meager meal and got our clothes-- two sets of everything-- and I remember, I still had some high-- shoes with high-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, with high laces.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I put those on, even though it was summertime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when it got dark, I held on to my mother's hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And we walked into the stillness of the night towards the river.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We ended up in the river.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, shots rang out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
